fields.name: single_wall_boxes
fields.description: Medium duty single wall stock cartons are made from high quality fluted cardboard. This economical range is ideal for protecting goods in storage or transit. They are conveniently supplied flat packed in a free outer box in packs of 20. The majority of our range also include multi-score heights which allows the height of the box to be reduced to a pre-scored crease.  This is a simple way to efficiently pack varying height products securely without the need for multiple box sizes. The additional benefit of these boxes is that it reduces the need for expensive void fill, which is also better for the environment. All our boxes are measured Length x Width x Height.

fields.name: double_wall_long_boxes
fields.description: Our double walled, long, top opening, cardboard boxes come in four different sizes to allow for the more unusual, long, products that you may have to package. Heavy duty single wall stock cartons are made from high quality fluted cardboard. This range is ideal for protecting goods in storage or transit. They are conveniently supplied flat packed in a free outer box in packs of 10. All our boxes are measured Length x Width x Height.

fields.name: bottle_boxes
fields.description: Our moulded pulp and corrugate bottle protectors are a safe and eco-friendly solution for  transportation of bottled goods, providing unrivalled protection throughout the shipping process. These Safansound Bottle Protectors are a combination of an outer transit case and a pulp clam-shell inner, designed to protect bottles and other glass products through the UK postal service. These Bottle Boxes are Biodegradable, Recycleable, and easy to use. Our range of pulp postal boxes for wine, spirits and champagne bottles are available in Single Packs, Double Packs, Treble Packs, Six Packs, Twelve Packs, and a special Champagne Bottle (1L) size.

fields.name: bubble_wrap
fields.description: Bubble wrap rolls are ideal for the cushion protection of delicate and fragile items while in transit. Please note that orders over 4 rolls may arrive as separate consignments.

fields.name: bubble_bags
fields.description: We stock five sizes of self seal bubble wrap bags. Our bubble bags are manufactured by Jiffy using high quality bubble cushioning film with a nylon additive. The unique nylon barrier provides an air-tight seal for long term cushion protection. A self-seal closure is standard for all bubble bags. Just remove the release tape and fold over the top flap to make a seal.

fields.name: document_wallets
fields.description: Self-adhesive polythene envelopes that carry invoices, advice notes or packing lists on the outside of parcels. These document enclosed wallets are waterproof, oil proof and secure.
